    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "1. Per ACAC-S 515.1 the following report is submitted on a matter",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "which may become of National Interest. [REDACTED] and his CoPilot",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "[REDACTED] have stated that on August 4, 1947 they sighted and followed a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "flying saucer Northwest of Bethel Alaska. This object was bigger than the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Douglas DC-3 they were flying, crossed their course at right angles to them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "It was flying at an Altitude of one thousand feet. They swung in behind it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "and followed it at an air speed of one hundred seventy miles per hour but",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "it was out of sight in four minutes. They state the object was smooth",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "surfaced and streamlined with no visible means of propulsion whatever.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "b6",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "2. It is realized that the Fourth Air Force claims there are no such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "things but [REDACTED] for Al Jones flying service and is",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "not a man given to exaggerations. In view of the excellent reputation of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "[REDACTED] and the fact that no one here doubts in the least but that he",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "actually saw this object, this report is turned in for any action deemed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "necessary by your office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
